# Dental Clinic Flyer Walkthrough

I have successfully designed and implemented the A4 dental clinic flyer focusing on preventive dentistry.

## Visual Preview
![Flyer Preview](/flyer_preview_1769460353987.png)

## Design Features
- **Japanese Aesthetic**: Used "Noto Serif JP" and "Noto Sans JP" for a professional and trustworthy look.
- **Color Scheme**: Mint Green (#5BC8AC) for cleanliness and Warm Beige (#FCFAF2) for approachability.
- **Content**:
    - **Header**: Captures attention with a smiling multi-generational photo and the message "The happiness of eating with your own teeth for a lifetime."
    - **Merits**: Clearly explains the benefits of regular checkups (Early Detection, Professional Care, Systemic Health).
    - **Call to Action**: Encourages easy booking.

## Files Created
- [flyer/index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8f20862f-d938-47c5-981d-2e4568fa21dd/flyer/index.html): The main structure.
- [flyer/style.css](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8f20862f-d938-47c5-981d-2e4568fa21dd/flyer/style.css): Styling for A4 layout and print optimization.
- `flyer/images/`: Contains the generated main visual and logo.

## How to Print
1.  Open [flyer/index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8f20862f-d938-47c5-981d-2e4568fa21dd/flyer/index.html) in your browser.
2.  Press `Ctrl + P` (or Cmd + P).
3.  Ensure "Background graphics" is checked in the print settings.
4.  Set paper size to A4.
